data.description: Buyer unable to secure financing. Quick closing possible. Move in ready brick row home with a large living room, large dinning room, kitchen with updated cabinets that leads to a back room with storage and or office. Half bath. Kitchen exits to a nice size fenced yard with a detached 1 car garage. This home is 2/3 bedrooms with a large master with 2 spacious closets and hard wood flooring on second floor. 3rd floor can be 2 more bedrooms and or office space. Clear CO from the City of Allentown.
